{"tid":2501420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"總選舉事務主任可以強迫任何地方成為票站，不遵從可被罰款一萬！","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T12:32:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"04653c55dcbad2af07aa72df8269bb00e7a1a125","tid":2501420,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587407-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587407-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=75d210ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587407-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4e0e5f17\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587407-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會繼續審議完善選舉制度的綜合修訂條例草案。當局建議加入新條款，總選舉事務主任可以規定任何目標處所用作投票站或點票站，任何人如果無遵從規定，可被罰款一萬元。<br />\n<br />\n有議員認為罰則太輕，建議將有關規定列為發牌條件；亦有議員批評有學校及社福團體不借出地方是缺乏社會責任，應公開有關機構的名字。"},{"pid":"9975d3eb3a7338c6397586f8274e4215c3c0aa58","tid":2501420,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"共產既精粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ecb5a621b20d64857ebb47135728f5c628aef3","tid":2501420,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:51:19.000Z","msg":"我屋企都得？"},{"pid":"c57bf597ebfbe57afe3ec6e4a08e88b30ef2da64","tid":2501420,"uid":279298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"只可以投支持建制或者沒有意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dda61906be99e02ff6710f70bc3d7f4e8254e9f","tid":2501420,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1ecb5a621b20d64857ebb47135728f5c628aef3","tid":2501420,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1